
	Worlds of Legend HD Fix by Tue Brisson


	Before you can use this you must install WHDLoad and Reloc
	from the whdload package. (DIC is needed to get savefiles.)
	The tools must be available via the path.


	Required memory:	0.5 MB ChipMem
				0.5 MB FastMem

	To quit press:		DEL


	To import "Legend" characters into "Worlds of Legend":
	First, get the "Legend HD Fix" archive, then use the "Legend Saves" installer.
	Now copy one or more of the savefiles (named LEGEND0..9) to your
	"Worlds of Legend" drawer.
	Now you can import your old characters.


	For problems contact:	morbidus@usa.net
	Full whdload package:	aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?.lha
	Other installs:		http://www.fh-zwickau.de/~jah/whdload.html
